d 'OKPRESERVE': module to implement nested preserve and restore for data workflows
d
d      okpreserve and okrestore provide a solution for managing
d complex, multi-level data transformations in Stata. These
d commands    enable true nested preservation of data states, which
d is essential when your analysis involves multiple stages of data 
d   aggregation, filtering, and transformation.    Unlike Stata's
d built-in preserve/restore, which do not support nesting,
d okpreserve/okrestore maintain a stack of saved data	 states.
d This allows you to work with different levels of data granularity
d within a single do-file. 
d
d KW: data management
d KW: preserve
d KW: restore
d
d Requires: Stata version 19
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260716
d
d Author: Vikrant V. Kamble,   University of Delaware
d Support: email vvkamble@@udel.edu
d
f okpreserve.ado
f okrestore.ado
f okpreserve.sthlp
f ../t/test_okpreserve.do
